Catch Up.
Get Ahead.
Whether you’re already enrolled at UIC or you attend another university, use the flexibility of summer at UIC to achieve your goals.

Lighten your fall or spring course load
Stay on track to graduation
Study with nationally recognized faculty

Choose from nearly 300 courses. Enroll in the 4-week session, 8-week session, or both.


Summer Courses
A preview of 2023 courses will be available in Dec. In the meantime, see what courses were offered this past summer.
Email list
Sign up for our email list to be notified about 2023 course info and (if you are a visiting student) when the summer application becomes available.
 


2023 Key Dates
4-Week Session: May 15 – June 9
8-Week Session: June 12 – August 4
Summer Tuition and Fees
Check out the per credit hour rate for summer 2022 tuition and fees. The rate for summer 2023 will be available in January.
 











 
